Package diewald_fluid

Class Summary
Fluid2D this class handles all the parameters of the fluid (CPU / GPU version).
Fluid2D_CPU this class creates a 2D-fluid-solver that runs completely on the CPU.
Fluid2D_GPU this class creates a 2D-fluid-solver that runs completely on the GPU.
